<p>
<lb n="1"/>śubhamastu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavarṣaṁbulu 1457 Agunēṁṭi jayasaṁvatsara caitra śu 15 Ādivārānanu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="2"/>śrījaganāthani Ājñanu tammumudaliṁgāri kumāruṁḍu kūrmumudali <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> bhairavadvārānanu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="3"/>hanumaṁttuni pratiṣṭhacēsi <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śiṁhyādri Apparubhaṁḍārānaku <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> saskāniṭaṁkkālu 50 peṭi Iṁdukaḷaṁ 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>trānaku hanumaṁtuni bhōgānaku di 1 ki Appālu 2 ki du 1 Iṁduku dalamubiyyaṁ sō 3 minumulu so 1 neI sō <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> ceraka
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḍaṁpa © <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> vuppu mā 2 verasu Iṁttavaṭukunnu du 1 vo<unclear>ra</unclear>yākuṁḍa vokhaṭi 1 ki biyyaṁ A 2 kudu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> verasu du 1 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> valna vecamu
<lb n="6"/>yī dēvaraṁ būjacēsi naṁbārki nīḷu pūlutecci Aṁduku sahāgānu vorayā 1 ki du <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Appamu sagānku du <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> I bhogaṁteci
<lb n="7" break="no"/>suvāriki Appamu sagānaku du <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> verasu duggāṇi vōI nirmālya bikkādammamu lekhkanu Apparu bhaṁḍārānaku Āyaṁcēsukoni
<lb n="8" break="no"/>vārū <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatruṇāpi kṛtō dharmmaḥ pālaniyyō manīṣibhiḥ śatrurēva hi śatru<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> syāt dharmmaśśatru<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>na kasyacit <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svadattāḥ
<lb n="9"/>paradattā vā nāśayaṁtti haraṁti ca ṣaṣṭirvarṣasahasrāṇi viṣṭhāyāṁ jāyatē krimiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>
